sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor G as Guest
    participant V as View (Login.html)
    participant P as Presenter (Auth.js)
    participant A as API (login.php)
    participant M as Model (UserModel.php)
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    Note over G, V: Scenario: User enters credentials

    G->>V: Fills Email and Password
    G->>V: Clicks on "Login"
    
    V->>P: 'submit' event
    activate P
    P->>P: Validation (Non-empty fields)
    
    Note over P, A: Sending sensitive data via POST (HTTPS)
    P->>A: FETCH POST /api/login (JSON body)
    activate A
    
    A->>M: login(email, password)
    activate M
    
    M->>DB: SELECT hash, id FROM users WHERE email = ?
    activate DB
    DB-->>M: Return Hash & UserData
    deactivate DB
    
    M->>M: password_verify(password, hash)
    
    alt Valid Password
        M->>M: session_start()
        M-->>A: Return Success + UserRole
        A-->>P: JSON { success: true, redirect: '/dashboard' }
        P->>V: window.location.href = '/dashboard'
        V->>G: Show Dashboard
    else Invalid Password
        M-->>A: Return False
        A-->>P: JSON { success: false, error: "Invalid credentials" }
        P->>V: Show error "Login failed"
        V->>G: Show error "Login failed"
    end
    
    deactivate M
    deactivate A
    deactivate P
